ENTRY            D8119   20260410   20260528   20260528       D152
SUBENT        D8119001   20260410   20260528   20260528       D152
BIB                 11         23
TITLE      Revealing nucleon-nucleon correlation effects through
            sub-Coulomb transfer reactions in 92Mo+54Fe
AUTHOR     (T.Mijatovic, S.Szilner, L.Corradi, F.Galtarossa,
            G.Pollarolo, G.Colucci, E.Fioretto, A.Goasduff,
            A.Gottardo, D.Jelavic Malenica, M.Milin, G.Montagnoli,
            D.Montanari, N.Soic, A.M.Stefanini,
            J.J.Valiente Dobon)
INSTITUTE  (3CRORBZ,2ITYPAD,2ITYUPV,2ITYTUR,3POLWWA,3CROZAG,
            2SPNVAL)
REFERENCE  (J,PL/B,872,140085,2026)
FACILITY   (LINAC,2ITYPAD) PIAVE-ALPI accelerator complex, or
            Tandem+ALPI (346 MeV irradiation)
SAMPLE     (26-FE-54,ENR=0.999)
           54Fe (100 ug/cm2) consisted of a strip of 2 mm
            sandwiched between C layers (20 ug/cm2)
METHOD     (TOF,EDE)
DETECTOR   (MCPLT,MAGSP,PPAC,IOCH) for detection of Fe-like recoil
           (SIBAR) Monitor for absolute normalization.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical uncertainty
STATUS     (TABLE,,T.Mijatovic+,J,PL/B,872,140085,2026) Figure 3
           (APRVD) Approved by Tea Mijatovic (2026-04-10)
HISTORY    (20260223R) Received by e-mail from T.Mijatovic
           (20260408C) M.Odsuren, N.Otsuka
ENDBIB              23
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           26
SUBENT        D8119002   20260410   20260528   20260528       D152
BIB                  2          6
REACTION   (42-MO-92(26-FE-54,X)ELEM/MASS,,IPA)
COMMENT    *Tea Mijatovic (2026-04-10):
           The central PRISMA angle is 22 degrees, and the
            acceptance is +/-6 degrees in theta. Integration was
            done in this forward-angle region, that covers most
            of the transfer flux at these beam energies.
ENDBIB               6
COMMON               2          3
ANG        ANG-RSL-HW
ADEG       ADEG
 22.        6.
ENDCOMMON            3
